TITLE: Using mergeAnimateProp in Child Components with useMotiPressable
DESCRIPTION: Example of using mergeAnimateProp in child components with the useMotiPressable hook, enabling composition of pressable interactions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nandorojo/moti/blob/master/docs/docs/interactions/merge.md#2025-04-15_snippet_6

