TITLE: Configuring Babel for react-native-linear-gradient
DESCRIPTION: Babel configuration to alias the skeleton imports for react-native-linear-gradient usage.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nandorojo/moti/blob/master/docs/docs/skeleton.mdx#2025-04-15_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
// babel.config.js
module.exports = function (api) {
  api.cache(true)
  return {
    plugins: [
      [
        'module-resolver',
        {
          root: ['./'],
          alias: {
            'moti/skeleton': 'moti/skeleton/react-native-linear-gradient',
          },
        },
      ],
    ],
  }
}
```

